                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Candies' residue gives Aezar an especially strong grip on her greataxe, which grants her a +2 circumstance bonus to her Reflex DC against attempts to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Disarm] her.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
